00:23:57,716 --> 00:24:00,117
Cui Yi only has one son.

475
00:24:01,756 --> 00:24:02,877
And,

476
00:24:03,276 --> 00:24:05,197
he came to my residence himself.

477
00:24:06,316 --> 00:24:09,677
