539
00:28:55,357 --> 00:28:57,357
Young Master, you can take your bath now.

540
00:28:57,476 --> 00:28:57,956
Okay.

541
00:29:26,720 --> 00:29:27,760
Someone is on the rooftop.

542
00:29:28,820 --> 00:29:29,556
